POST http://localhost:8080/api/recommend


It should accept JSON with fields:

json
Copy code
{
  "name": "John",
  "age": 25,
  "bmi": 22.5,
  "preferences": "milk,banana",
  "budget": 2500
}

And return a response like:

json
Copy code
[
  { "name": "Banana", "price": 30, "calories": 90 },
  { "name": "Oats", "price": 120, "calories": 200 }
]
